review_blob: i do not understand what all the hoopla is about this beer and the brewery in general,every time i drink one of there beers i hate it.
I heard good things about this beer, but it let me down not very flavorful ,overly hoppy and just plain didnt taste good.
i have had this beer numerous times and have been disappointed ever time i had it,at least its consistent.
i have not seen this beer in our area for some time,extremely well balanced,one of the best pales out there.
I Think id rather drink out of the Neshaminy creek than ever try to drink this beer again.
beer_name: Neshaminy Creek Juicy Ale With Nugget (JAWN)
